		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Today I am limber­ing up to attend the Dutch geek fest­ival, Observe Hack Make (<a href="https://program.ohm2013.org/"><span class="caps">OHM</span> 2013</a>). A lot of talks from whis­tleblowers, sci­ent­ists, geeks, futur­ists and bleed­ing edge tech people. The visionaries?</p>
<p>You decide — all talks will be live streamed and avail­able after­wards. Enjoy!</p>
