												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/big-brother" title="View all posts in Big Brother" rel="category tag">Big Brother</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/civil-liberties" title="View all posts in Civil Liberties" rel="category tag">Civil Liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/democracy" title="View all posts in Democracy" rel="category tag">Democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/ip" title="View all posts in IP" rel="category tag">IP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/it" title="View all posts in IT" rel="category tag">IT</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/open-source" title="View all posts in Open source" rel="category tag">Open source</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/police" title="View all posts in Police" rel="category tag">Police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/politics" title="View all posts in Politics" rel="category tag">Politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/surveillance" title="View all posts in Surveillance" rel="category tag">Surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/technology" title="View all posts in Technology" rel="category tag">Technology</a>			</span>
									<span class="sep"> | </span>
							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/big-brother" rel="tag">Big Brother</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/copyright" rel="tag">copyright</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/cory-doctorow" rel="tag">Cory Doctorow</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/eben-moglen" rel="tag">Eben Moglen</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intellectual-property" rel="tag">intellectual property</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/p2p" rel="tag">P2P</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/technology-2" rel="tag">technology</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/telstra" rel="tag">Telstra</a>			</span>
						
