				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/cctv" rel="tag">CCTV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/charles-stross" rel="tag">Charles Stross</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/civil-liberties-2" rel="tag">civil liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/drones" rel="tag">drones</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/face-recognition" rel="tag">face recognition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/facebook" rel="tag">Facebook</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/google" rel="tag">Google</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/police-2" rel="tag">police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/scorpion-stare" rel="tag">scorpion stare</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/trapwire" rel="tag">Trapwire</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
