	<article id="post-29" class="post-29 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-big-brother category-intelligence category-it category-spies category-surveillance tag-bugs tag-eavesdropping tag-geek tag-humour tag-intelligence-2 tag-spies-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/10/geek-humour.html" title="Permalink to Geek humour" rel="bookmark">Geek humour</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/10/geek-humour.html" title="14:11" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2011-10-04T14:11:35+00:00" pubdate>October 4, 2011</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/10/geek-humour.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Well, it made me laugh:</p>
<p><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/6a00e55090303188330153920f5ab1970b-popup.html" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="I_know_youre_listening" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00e55090303188330153920f5ab1970b" src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/6a00e55090303188330153920f5ab1970b-500wi.png" title="I_know_youre_listening" /></a></p>
<p>Of course, I’ve never done this myself.….</p>
<p>More of these excel­lent car­toons can be found at <a href="http://xkcd.org/" target="_self">xkcd​.org</a>.</p>
