				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/bamford" rel="tag">Bamford</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/echelon" rel="tag">Echelon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/gchq" rel="tag">GCHQ</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi5" rel="tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/nsa" rel="tag">NSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/privacy" rel="tag">privacy</a>			</span>
						
